{
  "texts": [
    "It describes the research design, the sampling method, the tools for data collection, and the data analysis method selected.",
    "Issues of data quality and protection of participants are noted as well.",
    "The study design ensures reliability, validity, and ethics throughout the research.",
    "Research design is an action plan linking research questions to data collection, measures, and analysis (Creswell & Creswell, 2017).",
    "It integrates various parts of the research logically and consistently to ensure its credibility and dependability."
  ]
}